 To ask a girl to marry you, ask her companionship, relate your reasons for desiring to enter into a marriage-like relationship with her and consequently, ask her to be your spouse. After that, one should be prepared to wait a few days or a few weeks, to see if she shows up at the church with a ring on her finger. If she doesn't want to marry you, this is a sign that you may want to spend more time courting her. If she
